{"tid":462840,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大肚婆同事當自己係VIP","createTime":"2017-11-09T02:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T08:19:52.000Z","uid":44377,"like":639,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d376fc8bd367ffce460f4a24a8b279560bc517","tid":462840,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"最近有個同事大左肚, 咁無咩野本身都係一件值得開心既事<br />\n但佢自從大左肚後開始當左自己係VIP, 覺得自己係公司大撚晒<br />\n<br />\n我公司放左工後都有機會收CALL既, 咁我地採取輪更制, 每人做兩星期ON CALL咁SHIFT<br />\n個大肚婆自從知道自己有左後, 偷偷地將自己係個更表到remove左, 完全無同任何人講過, 包括supervisor都無, 我地check返更表先知佢自己偷偷地remove左, 所以個更表亂撚晒, 有D同事可能就左時間放假既而家又要再夾過, 同supervisor反映返件事, 個supervisor怕佢恃住自己大肚搞事所以不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後個大肚婆同事恃住自己大肚咩都要人幫, 例如PRINTER換紙都話重, 怕整到個肚, 虧佢好意思講得出口, 明明換A4紙都唔駛擒高擒低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次個大肚婆有個會係星期六上午開, 咁條八婆又用自己大肚之類既藉口叫另一個同事代佢去, 咁個位同事可能都約左人所以好唔願意幫佢頂, 最後俾人係背後唱咩 &quot;人地大肚都唔肯幫手&quot; 之類既說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他小事例如遲到早退呢D唔駛講啦, 佢而家每日返工都係有限度工作, 一係上baby condom睇野<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母原來有左真係無敵, 無人敢嘈佢同話佢, 廢事俾人係背後唱蝦大肚婆同埋怕佢搞事<br />\n本身都可能體諒佢大肚真係會辛苦, 幫下手都OK, 但唔係奉旨要人幫囉, 日日係到呃飯食等出糧收錢, 佢個肚我地又無份, 根本應該叫返佢老公黎做就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d570290aaec5abc9fe2cf73a01335750ef9837","tid":462840,"uid":87506,"like":6,"dislike":547,"score":-541,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"互相幫忙姐... 除非佢語氣真係好差啦"},{"pid":"361b898e4fc8818f3649454beddacdc5cff121b3","tid":462840,"uid":83063,"like":207,"dislike":4,"score":203,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"我都覺大肚婆恃住個肚好黑人憎<br />\n通常呢啲生出黎都會少/多左啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eb049921600bf522aca084fcd03a63e366f3ac","tid":462840,"uid":8410,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:57:12.000Z","msg":"大肚婆黑人憎的話留係公司係特別多意外的"},{"pid":"3b73f3807c8c837b96510da65dfb5079d8df3c81","tid":462840,"uid":44377,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>互相幫忙姐... 除非佢語氣真係好差啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係唔幫, 係佢奉旨要人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且點樣互相幫忙, 佢有撚幫返我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814e4386d2a122f1ded4caf41287267f44dcd6bf","tid":462840,"uid":108329,"like":338,"dislike":6,"score":332,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"同佢細細聲講：信唔信我一野打爆你個肚..嘿嘿..."},{"pid":"f6d154dcd3eedcfa85a071be63e1647d66b2fd7f","tid":462840,"uid":29080,"like":88,"dislike":3,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢細細聲講：信唔信我一野打爆你個肚..嘿嘿...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12d60e97b4152db0cea7f6248e8ae64004e96c5","tid":462840,"uid":15394,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"個大肚婆係咪短髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有個大肚婆同事，同你講既一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94742e011c419c0e249bdcd78b145615a8e6db79","tid":462840,"uid":86893,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tvbmademeopenthis.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/tvb-pregnant.jpg?w=510&amp;h=286\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftvbmademeopenthis.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F01%2Ftvb-pregnant.jpg%3Fw%3D510%26h%3D286&h=b98905a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e380f838783faad0394b8c753fd4b9a7afc3b8fe","tid":462840,"uid":133,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:12:11.000Z","msg":"你唔好搞呀, 一陣比人去平機會告鳩你就仆街."},{"pid":"ca3c63c08a80127e3b8478b779bd9b2