"c291695a32494a1103fc1baff7e3db4dcf12e695","tid":462840,"uid":123969,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"依啲要好似日本想老員工自己離職咁困係間房無電腦唔比玩電話淨係用紙筆做啲超重複性工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d57d839871624d124180ac580d10b8b2faf3cc","tid":462840,"uid":23629,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有佐的確係大曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯<br />\n唔好話大肚果時<br />\n佢放完產假之後返黎都係大曬<br />\n郁一郁就同你講: 平機會見"},{"pid":"6d1ba07a55c0b0248b7202f3f879d11b79107bbb","tid":462840,"uid":4696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依啲要好似日本想老員工自己離職咁困係間房無電腦唔比玩電話淨係用紙筆做啲超重複性工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 電腦咁多輻射 影響bb就唔係幾好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc58386885b535588b42ca981090d7cecaec9935","tid":462840,"uid":44377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依啲要好似日本想老員工自己離職咁困係間房無電腦唔比玩電話淨係用紙筆做啲超重複性工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd supervisor都唔敢郁佢, 怕佢搞事, 一陣又平機會又呢樣個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b724369ffb1d5c066ff3029604592425d59d5c38","tid":462840,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無咁撚大晒<br />\n可以係更表到remove 自己不如直情佢編更啦<br />\n老細有份中出佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家情況都差唔多架啦, 有D咩事就叫其他同事幫佢頂<br />\n你唔幫, 背後就俾人話蝦大肚婆"},{"pid":"a46ed2cebbe538ff87a0da2f69c14acbc8a323e3","tid":462840,"uid":17928,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"平時塊八達通都好使好用，依家仲多一張小童，唔VIP 就奇啦，加埋平機會加持，邊有人夠膽challenge 佢"},{"pid":"df6461ed496d952f494d56559e2d704c6e6be872","tid":462840,"uid":156121,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"俾大肚婆同事玩倒真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係編更既有更表 行政好少少既點會俾佢刪倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔番既咪曠佢工<br />\n<br />\n呢個case唔係佢大肚既問題 係佢恃寵生嬌囉<br />\n你老細呢D少事都怕 呢間公司真係冇乜前途"},{"pid":"c51ed67abc38665f7dd593acad89c320f9647dfc","tid":462840,"uid":129521,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喂八婆 你個肚我有份架？</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"dbd4195899f342c424b3f641b45a755a29331270","tid":462840,"uid":56716,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"有啲大肚婆真係好乞人憎，當正自己係女皇咁，大家咁高咁大，見你大肚咪唔使你做啲擔擔抬抬野，但仲要得寸進尺，樣樣都要人就哂佢，乜都唔做話佢就賴個肚，簡單野都唔做要聲控同事做，點解大咗肚嘅女人會咁仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e632fbf45eefa6a46c6e710d46513f4c05fc44","tid":462840,"uid":44377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾大肚婆同事玩倒真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係編更既有更表 行政好少少既點會俾佢刪倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔番既咪曠佢工<br />\n<br />\n呢個case唔係佢大肚既問題 係佢恃寵生嬌囉<br />\n你老細呢D少事都怕 呢間公司真係冇乜前途</blockquote><br />\n更表個到其實係已經放左工, 不過我地有機會要ON CALL做野, 所以係輪更咁去做, 收到CALL做野係CLAIM返OT錢<br />\n<br />\n更表就係一個EXCEL放係SHARE FOLDER架咋, 自己圍內輪更去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15244fb0e3d1c65d4e079dc983516eb70c0e3955","tid":462840,"uid":32114,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個大肚婆係咪短髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有個大肚婆同事，同你講既一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀？<br />\n咁你嗰個大肚婆係咪女人黎架？<br />\n係嘅呢度相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2506405fc13c49a91a7b206f567364139195d1","tid":462840,"uid":150899,"like":3,"dislike":101,"score":-98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"以家d 後生女，没我地个年代甘好，甘的死样都做到人地阿媽"},{"pid":"a16b33c10c0fe79874124ce3efc56ee59a29cdf1","tid":462840,"uid":106247,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有佐的確係大曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯<br />\n唔好話大肚果時<br />\n佢放完產假之後返黎都係大曬<br />\n郁一郁就同你講: 平機會見</blockquote><br />\n平機會無牙老虎黎<br />\n怕咩"},{"pid":"c43b0ee836bb261ad037b974a0ad58946c54c48b","tid":462840,"uid":12269,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個大肚婆係咪短髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有個大肚婆同事，同你講既一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀？<br />\n咁你嗰個大肚婆係咪女人黎架？<br />\n係嘅呢度相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2186ec580d04b62d622aeacdea9fdb109975b9c","tid":462840,"uid":29858,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以家d 後生女，没我地个年代甘好，甘的死样都做到人地阿媽</blockquote><br />\n( Show Blocked User - bigblueshark )"},{"pid":"ee58b11de6cccfdbe4aa1d7f3c0c71dcd53d2c15","tid":462840,"uid":42009,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"呢D大肚婆真係好Q賤！<br />\n試過有次無乜留意佢同個friend自己攝埋黎我坐梗張長櫈，我玩手機已經無乜理佢因為我都等緊我朋友買野食返黎先坐底！<br />\n明明我坐低先既，條八婆仲越迫越過好似想趕走埋我咁，<br />\n我開頭又無乜留意佢，後尾先聽到佢同friend講：⋯⋯大肚婆都唔讓⋯⋯<br />\n之後我先望一望佢，小喇叭根本都未見肚鬼知你大肚咩臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我說諗起連登名句：我又無份中出你，做乜全世界都要就曬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5996cf851e911d08c5da68b3dccfd2c2d1dda67d","tid":46